 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。有數支球隊表示對洛·侯斯有興趣，包括[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]及[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]<ref>{{cite news
 | language = en
 | title = Duo track Hulse
 | url = http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_2268130,00.html
 | publisher = Sky Sports
 | date = 2003-06-12
 | accessdate = 2009-03-16}}</ref>，其中與克魯一同升級的[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]據報出價約75萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]接近成功收購<ref>{{cite news
 | language = en
 | title = Crewe and Cardiff agree Hulse fee
 | url = http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_2268896,00.html
 | publisher = Sky Sports
 | date = 2003-06-23
 | accessdate = 2009-03-16}}</ref>，惟一心希望加盟[[英超|英超]]球隊的洛·侯斯無意加盟「藍鳥」<ref>{{cite news
 | language = en
 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crewe_alexandra/3002004.stm 
 | title = Hulse snubs Cardiff
 | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
 | date = 2003-07-01
 | accessdate = 2009-03-14}}</ref>。西布朗及[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]先後出價<ref>{{cite news
 | language = en
 | title = Duo bid for Hulse
 | url = http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2269825,00.html
