 | accessdate = 2009-03-16}}</ref>。雖然克魯與[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]談妥價錢<ref>{{cite news
 | language = en
 | title = Lions agree Hulse fee
 | url = http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11735_2270024,00.html
