 }}</ref>。

===西布朗===
2003年7月8日[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]願意提價後再次向克魯求購洛·侯斯<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2270098,00.html |title=Baggies make new Hulse bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-07-08 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090150/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2270098,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，結果以初步75萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]（可增加到100萬英鎊）獲取洛·侯斯首肯加盟<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/3055657.stm |title=Baggies bag duo |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-07-11 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208173047/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/3055657.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2270428,00.html |title=Albion secure Hulse |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-07-11 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145020/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2270428,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他於2003年8月9日作客4-1擊敗[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|華素爾]]首次披甲上陣，三日後在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]主場4-0擊敗[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|賓福特]]時梅開二度<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/3133189.stm |title=West Brom 4-0 Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-08-12 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2017-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518034832/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/3133189.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而三日後於主場4-1大勝[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]中射入一球在聯賽「開齋」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3137517.stm |title=West Brom 4-1 Burnley |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-08-16 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172003/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3137517.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。洛·侯斯其後分別在對[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3084084.stm |title=West Brom 4-1 Ipswich |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-09-13 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213629/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3084084.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3211065.stm |title=Rotherham 0-3 West Brom |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-10-25 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307124111/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3211065.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3232985.stm |title=West Ham 3-4 West Brom |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-11-08 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227081729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3232985.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>再梅開二度，於11月初在各項比賽合共射入12球，是西布朗爭取升級的重要成員。但其後狀態急轉直下，更於2004年1月17日作客[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]時於上半場27分鐘因嚴重犯規被直接[[紅牌|紅牌]]罰離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3385177.stm |title=Burnley 1-1 West Brom |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-01-17 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307015751/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3385177.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2288883,00.html |title=Megson steps up striker search |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2004-01-19 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309130335/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2288883,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。直到3月6日對[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]才再射入下半季唯一的入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3495450.stm |title=West Brom 3-0 Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307202836/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3495450.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然如此，西布朗仍然獲得[[英格蘭足球聯賽|甲組聯賽〈第二級〉]]亞軍升級到[[英超|英超]]，而洛·侯斯亦以13球成為球隊首席射手。

由於西布朗在季後簽入[[罗伯特·厄恩肖|安梳爾]]（Robert Earnshaw）、[[謝菲·賀斯菲特|賀斯菲特]]及[[恩万科沃·卡努|簡奴]]等鋒線球員，而洛·侯斯的排名甚至在老將[[奇雲·金寶|奇雲·金寶]]（Kevin Campbell）之後，在英超沒有多少次登場機會，2004年10月14日[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]要求借用備受冷落的洛·侯斯卻被領隊[[加里·麥格森|加利·麥臣]]（Gary Megson）拒絕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/3743622.stm |title=Stoke fail in move for WBA pair |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-10-14 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307092025/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/3743622.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[2004年至2005年英格蘭超級聯賽|2004/05年球季]]上半季洛·侯斯只獲5次聯賽、1次[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]及1次[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]合共7次上陣，全部以後補身份入替，入球掛零。在冬季轉會窗重開，史篤城有意收購洛·侯斯<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/4196737.stm |title=WBA striker makes move to Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-01-21 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307125034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/4196737.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，兩隊已同意120萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的轉會費<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2324602,00.html |title=Baggies accept Hulse bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2004-01-21 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042117/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2324602,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但洛·侯斯在與家人及經理人商討後拒絕加盟<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/4203007.stm |title=Striker Hulse rejects Stoke move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-01-24 |accessdate=2009-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307223517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/4203007.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2324767,00.html |title=Hulse shuns City move |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2004-01-24 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090155/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2324767,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===列斯聯===
2005年2月9日洛·侯斯成功獲外借到[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]3個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4233277.stm |title=Hulse completes Leeds loan switch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-02-09 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208170508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4233277.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2326380,00.html |title=Whites tie up Hulse deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-02-09 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145031/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2326380,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，加盟首仗在主場梅開二度協助球隊以3-1擊敗[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0,19764,11065_2391923,00.html |title=Hulse brace sinks Royals |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-02-12 |accessdate=2009-03-16}}</ref>，在加盟首4仗入4球後，列斯聯主帥[[奇雲·布力維爾|奇雲·布力維爾]]（Kevin Blackwell）表示希望在球季結束後將洛·侯斯正式收歸旗下<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2328826,00.html |title=Leeds eye Hulse deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-03-07 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309131849/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2328826,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他亦有意留效<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2332354,00.html |title=Hulse unsure of future |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-04-13 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090852/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2332354,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

借用期間洛·侯斯13次上陣及射入6球，布力維爾將落實洛·侯斯加盟作為來季組軍首要任務<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2334575,00.html |title=Blackwell hopeful of signings |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-05-07 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308043707/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2334575,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於5月9日以110萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]成功收購洛·侯斯<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4529127.stm |title=Leeds sign Baggies striker Hulse |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-09 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402215133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4529127.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2334856,00.html |title=Leeds secure Hulse deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-05-09 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309155702/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11698_2334856,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季前在[[挪威|挪威]]的首場[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]洛·侯斯弄傷[[足踝|足踝]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2341989,00.html |title=Hulse injury blow |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-07-14 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145425/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2341989,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而這個傷患整季一直困擾著他<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4374934.stm |title=Blackwell tribute to 'hero' Hulse |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-10-25 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402215841/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4374934.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後加上[[臀部|臀部]]受傷需要注射針藥止痛<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2357363,00.html |title=Hulse's hip hope |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-12-12 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308023430/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2357363,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他強忍痛楚<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2350957,00.html |title=More ankle woes for Hulse |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-10-11 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145428/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2350957,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，帶領球隊獲得聯賽第5位，有資格出爭升級附加賽，於附加賽準決賽次回合作客[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]先拔頭籌，在有兩人被逐下力保2-0勝果，累計3-1晉級決賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4972964.stm |title=Preston 0-2 Leeds (agg 1-3) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-08 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705153921/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4972964.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但決賽不幸以0-3負於[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]而無緣升級[[英超|英超]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2377622,00.html |title=Hulse not dwelling on loss |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-05-23 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090857/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2377622,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2005年至2006年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2005/06年球季]]洛·侯斯在各項比賽合共射入14球，包括聯賽對[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]的[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11696_2349849,00.html |title=Hulse hat-trick hands Leeds win |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-09-28 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308011115/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11696_2349849,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，與[[大衛·希利|大衛·希利]]併列球隊首席射手。

2006年4月6日洛·侯斯與[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|英格蘭職業足球運動員協會]]簽署經理人合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2372635,00.html |title=PFA welcome Hulse's signing |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-04-06 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145433/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_2372635,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===錫菲聯===
由於[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]未能升級，表現出色的洛·侯斯獲得不少其他球會垂青，先有[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]問價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/5097964.stm |title=Worthington keen on striker Hulse |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-06-20 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402220202/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/5097964.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再有[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]出價140萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2381689,00.html |title=Leeds reject Hulse offer |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-06-28 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2017-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216134710/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2381689,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，洛·侯斯表示樂意留隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2382967,00.html |title=Hulse happy with Whites |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-07-11 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2017-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216133239/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2382967,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終錫菲聯「加碼」到220萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]打動列斯聯，加上附加條款金額可提升到300萬英鎊，於2006年7月24日取得心頭好，洛·侯斯簽約效力三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/5211716.stm |title=Blades agree deal to sign Hulse |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-24 |accessdate=2009-03-16}}</ref>，希望再次在[[英超|英超]]比賽能夠證明自己的實力<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2385431,00.html |title=Hulse aims to prove himself |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-07-26 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2017-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216130601/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2385431,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 
 
[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]錫菲聯在缺席12年後重返[[英超|頂級聯賽]]，2006年8月19日首戰[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，洛·侯斯於下半場開賽後僅50秒即頂入先開紀錄，最後才被[[羅比·福勒|科拿]]憑[[十二碼|十二碼]]扳平1-1終場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4786663.stm |title=Sheffield United 1-1 Liverpool |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-19 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903154503/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4786663.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。洛·侯斯繼續有穩定的演出及入球，在首11場比賽射入4球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2395315,00.html |title=Hulse amazed by career turn |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-11-18 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144333/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2395315,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直到2007年3月3日對[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]射入一球，累計共射入8球，是球隊領先射手。

2007年3月17日錫菲聯作客[[史丹福橋球場|史丹福橋球場]]對[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6437227.stm |title=Chelsea 3-0 Sheff Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-17 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308004136/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6437227.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上半場25分鐘當洛·侯斯接應一個傳中球時與對方出迎的門將[[佩特·切赫|施治]]相撞，即時[[足踝|足踝]]骨折，洛·侯斯一動不動，在旁的施治嚇得用手掩眼不敢觀看，經過5分鐘處理傷處後才用擔架抬離場送往醫院。事後證實左腳雙重骨折<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2408678,00.html |title=Warnock reveals Hulse blow |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-03-19 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041437/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11683_2408678,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，施治就這宗意外表示歉意<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11668_2408728,00.html |title=Cech saddened by Hulse injury |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-03-19 |accessdate=2009-03-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310083047/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11668_2408728,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，洛·侯斯一度懷疑會就此「收山」，幸好手術成功，而曾有相同遭遇的[[阿蘭·史密斯|阿倫·史密夫]]亦對他加以鼓勵<ref>{{cite news
