}}</ref>。而洛·侯斯在10月份狀態登上高峰，於5場比賽射入4球，使他獲選為「英冠每月最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news
 |language    = en
 |url         = http://therams.co.uk/stories/prize-guy-rob-now-im-back-to-100
 |title       = Prize guy Rob - Now I'm back to 100%
 |publisher   = therams.co.uk
